{"tid":1351481,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下以前有個人教我被黑社會圍毆要點自保","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T20:21:09.000Z","uid":26000,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"dd949dc0d74f5a2a41d7e364aa69d80549162839","tid":1351481,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:32:51.000Z","msg":"經過元朗一事，香港人應該要知道「你不搞政治，政治最終亦會搞你」呢個道理<br />\n<br />\n我好相信類似事件會再次發生 與其被圍毆 不如學下點保護自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑社會嘅行動模式係一大堆人衝去圍人 以數量制勝<br />\n面對佢地講法律係冇意思 唯一方法係要人多過佢 大聲過佢 惡過佢<br />\n<br />\n元朗呢單明顯輸人又輸陣<br />\n<br />\n呢種情況可用以下方法自保<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一 唔好比人單捉</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">一旦落單 定必比人圍毆 下場悲慘</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果不幸落單 黑社會來勢洶洶 點算？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢個係最壞情況 唔洗諗住全身而退 只可求減低受傷<br />\n如果附近有牆角或者就咁有一面牆 盡量癡埋牆 縮埋個人 雙手護頭 唔好露出腹部同面部 如果有背囊或者其他袋可以用來擋 </span><br />\n<br />\n可能你會覺得咁做好on9 只會做沙包任人打 但如果唔咁做 嚐試跑走/突圍只會傷多兩錢重 因為任何角度都可以打到你 但癡埋牆可以令攻擊到你嘅人大幅減少 瞬間由1v10 變1v4<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信有唔少隱世高手自問好打得 但我絕對唔建議1打10 你拳腳功夫再好 都唔夠有架生嘅好打 更何況以一敵眾<br />\n<br />\n與其1打10 不如諗方法點變成10打1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />be water"},{"pid":"567401511f9f6477df07ed0fb5c36794723bf883","tid":1351481,"uid":95487,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:36:31.000Z","msg":"文宣方向！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔去搞政治<br />\n政治就會搞你</span><br />\n<br />\n全 民 皆 兵 ！</span>"},{"pid":"aac63959c926e9d9ed5a7effae0149495f97dde2","tid":1351481,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462015bf0d8adc03a5c824bf08114ed1043253e9","tid":1351481,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87ff6d8956f72bc2b71b3dd90c933d672943a825","tid":1351481,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:42:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d9d1866be582a92cd28563c4160a4e0cd0dea4","tid":1351481,"uid":20222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"有睇sparda就知佢地全部都係將背後交俾其他人<br />\n要打既時侯一定要組隊<br />\n有老人女人既時侯就幾個巴打圍住佢地然後用背狼擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然可以出下腳踢下佢地春袋<br />\n你知道男人一踢春袋真係痛到..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43e0f25813384d8acb826dfdb2e2db387a1c6c1","tid":1351481,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"推比多啲人見到"},{"pid":"fc09ff019a7c75c9f416582de389d3743bb6aa3b","tid":1351481,"uid":20222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f6d9d1866be582a92cd28563c4160a4e0cd0dea4","tid":1351481,"uid":20222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"有睇sparda就知佢地全部都係將背後交俾其他人<br />\n要打既時侯一定要組隊<br />\n有老人女人既時侯就幾個巴打圍住佢地然後用背狼擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然可以出下腳踢下佢地春袋<br />\n你知道男人一踢春袋真係痛到..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/551183185271898/posts/1066231177100427?s=100001065401561&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F551183185271898%2Fposts%2F1066231177100427%3Fs%3D100001065401561%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=4f48d4fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/551183185271898/posts/106623